{"id":3254,"date":"2023-10-02T08:59:29","date_gmt":"2023-10-01T21:59:29","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.stokefoiling.com\/?post_type=help_centre&#038;p=3254"},"modified":"2023-10-03T14:22:35","modified_gmt":"2023-10-03T03:22:35","slug":"pairing-your-remote","status":"publish","type":"help_centre","link":"https:\/\/www.stokefoiling.com\/help-centre\/installation\/pairing-your-remote\/","title":{"rendered":"Pairing Your Remote"},"content":{"rendered":"<p><strong>Your remote should come paired and calibrated from the factory, so only do the pairing steps if the remote isn\u2019t showing the connection signal strength bars in the top right of the display.<\/strong><\/p><p>Pairing the remote:<\/p><ol class=\"wp-block-list\" type=\"1\" start=\"1\"><li>With the main battery disconnected, power on the remote control.<\/li>\n\n<li>Hold down the power level\/menu button (the one with the 3 dots) until it displays \u201cPairing\u201d. You are now in menu mode.<\/li>\n\n<li>Hold down the menu button again to enter Pairing mode. Release the menu button.<\/li>\n\n<li>Attach the main battery to the main unit. You\u2019ll see a message that pairing succeeded on the remote and the signal strength will be shown.<\/li><\/ol><p>Very occasionally the pairing process takes 2 attempts, but you\u2019ll usually get it on the first try.<\/p><p>If the remote isn\u2019t unlocking or the throttle range isn\u2019t from 0-100% you can do a throttle calibration (unlikely that you\u2019ll need to do this as it would have been done before sending over):<\/p><ol class=\"wp-block-list\" type=\"1\" start=\"1\"><li>Power on the remote control.<\/li>\n\n<li>Hold down the power level\/menu button (the one with the 3 dots) until it displays \u201cPairing\u201d. You are now in menu mode.<\/li>\n\n<li>Click the 3 dots button again until \u201cThrottle Calibration\u201d is displayed.<\/li>\n\n<li>Hold down the menu button again to enter throttle calibration mode. Release the menu button.<\/li>\n\n<li>Pull the trigger through it\u2019s full range, then release the trigger.<\/li>\n\n<li>Click the Power button once to exit throttle calibration mode.<\/li>\n\n<li>Click the Power button again to exit the menu mode.<\/li><\/ol><p>Please don\u2019t hesitate to reach out if you are having any issues with this process.<\/p>","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Pairing your remote with our Stoke Foiling products is quick and easy.<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":0,"parent":0,"menu_order":0,"template":"","meta":{"_acf_changed":false,"rank_math_lock_modified_date":false,"footnotes":""},"class_list":["post-3254","help_centre","type-help_centre","status-publish","hentry","help_centre_category-installation"],"acf":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.stokefoiling.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/help_centre\/3254","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.stokefoiling.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/help_centre"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.stokefoiling.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/help_centre"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.stokefoiling.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"version-history":[{"count":5,"href":"https:\/\/www.stokefoiling.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/help_centre\/3254\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":3462,"href":"https:\/\/www.stokefoiling.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/help_centre\/3254\/revisions\/3462"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.stokefoiling.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=3254"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}